Adult.description: Hutton's Vireos are larger and move more slowly than Ruby-crowned Kinglets. They do not show a black bar on the wing below the white wingbar like Ruby-crowned Kinglets do.

Adult male.description: Golden-crowned Kinglets have a much bolder face pattern, with a yellow crown bordered by black stripes and a white stripe over the eye unlike Ruby-crowned, which have plain face with a white eyering.
